{"tid":572041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺中國要恢復帝制國力先會更強？","createTime":"2018-02-25T08:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T19:00:02.000Z","uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5927e8196fdc6d17275899d283895259cd7957","tid":572041,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"內地官媒周日（25日）報道，稱中共中央委員會建議修憲，刪除中華人民共和國國家主席、國家副主席的「不得連任多於兩屆」的規定。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，中共中央政治局已於上周六（24日）召開會議，決定在周一（26日）至周三（28日），在北京召開中共第十九屆中央委員會第三次全體會議。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係未來3日要可以表決<br />\n<br />\n快人快語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39b7b67e6846ea066396fddbc39565b4baf4b5b","tid":572041,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"你地支唔支持習大大既決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50463f9763b5daba0264a0ac56b93c6133a3e6b9","tid":572041,"uid":14918,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T16:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/003634_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F003634_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b0becda3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/004043_ed95ba321d1f287f88d0e32ec9f95e6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F004043_ed95ba321d1f287f88d0e32ec9f95e6e.png&h=3f385513&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b11b54de7c5829102d9b847b8f1b3b379b3b9127","tid":572041,"uid":14918,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201711/d20ab3d614d67c5f1a9753b81f379c24.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=